[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    324[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-team-initiated patient communication                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    325[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    326[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Conversation session bootstrap]                               │
