[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    336[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────── INPUT SAFETY + CONTINUOUS EMERGENCY SCREEN ───────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    337[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    338[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]            │
